T*
(  sample description) Tj
T*
(- The HSF sample requires students to verify the exact rules with official) Tj
T*
(  sources) Tj
T*
(- Federal aid tied to the FAFSA may have citizenship or eligible noncitizen) Tj
T*
(  requirements) Tj
T*
() Tj
T*
